          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X_\bullet ]]></fr:tex> be a simplicial topological space.
    The functors <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {H}^i(X_\bullet ,F^\bullet )]]></fr:tex> of <fr:em>cohomology with coefficients in the abelian sheaf <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[F^\bullet ]]></fr:tex> on <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X_\bullet ]]></fr:tex></fr:em> are the derived functors of the functor <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\Gamma ]]></fr:tex> (<fr:ref addr="hodge-theory-iii-5.1.13.1" href="hodge-theory-iii-5.1.13.1.xml" taxon="Equation" number="5.1.13.1" />).</fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
